### Key Design Decisions (Phase 2)

- **Code does enrichment + known patterns; Claude discovers from enriched data**
- **Enriched trade summary text** — full history in compact format for Claude to scan
- **Multi-scale temporal drift** — granular (12mo), phase (market-cycle), halves
- **Dynamic scenarios are additive** — 5 constant scenarios always shown + up to 3 personalized
- **No LLM calls in engines** — 100% deterministic; AI happens at conversation time
